name: Neny's Homestay

review 1:
Really awesome place to stay! In a nice and quite area and not too far from Keramas Beach. Neny was super kind and accomodating, provided us with a delicious breakfast everymorning and was more than happy to give advice on things to do in the area!
Highly recommend!
review 2: Great place to get away from the tourism and really see Bali. Located in a great place Surrounded by rice fields and a quick scooter to Tegenungan waterfall. Nenys place was very clean and the ac worked great. On top of this Neny went above and beyond to help me with a hospital trip, lent me her scooter, and translated phone calls for me. If you‚Äôre looking for somewhere quiet and in the ‚Äúcountryside‚Äù this is the place to be. Just make sure to rent a scooter in advance if you plan to run around without worrying about using her bike.

review 4: great place to stay so quiet and relaxing, I went to some waterfalls nearby , thanks Neny, I will come again definitely!
